reviews.customers_say: Customers love the sweater's sleeve detail weaving pattern and find it comfortable, soft, and warm for winter weather.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Looks great!
items.body: The shirt is a pretty color for Fall. It fits well and is soft. Read more
items.author: Gail

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice quality comfortable sweater.
items.body: Absolutely adorable, and much higher quality than I anticipated. I would say it runs pretty true to size I ordered a medium – sometimes I fluctuate between a medium and large and I feel like I could’ve gone either way. Read more
items.author: Heidi burke

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Comfy, one flaw
items.body: Super cute, very comfortable. There is a pretty harsh horizontal line down the middle of mine that won't come out. I've washed multiple times and done many things to get it out, but it's still there. The quality is really good for the price and the fit is true to size. Very durable (for the few times I've worn it) Read more
items.author: Cora

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Warm and Comfortable
items.body: Warm, great quality. It’s pretty heavy and comfortable. I got it in Apricot and in blue. The apricot did come with a strong smell but the blue one did not. I got a large. Love the fit. 5’ 1” 183 lbs 40 DDD Read more
items.author: D - Mom

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars extremely long sleeves
items.body: I love the color. I love the style. But the body of the sweater is too long for me. Worst of all, the sleeves are far too long. And since the sweater is heavy, I would not feel comfortable rolling up the cuffs. Sadly, I will be returning it. Read more
items.author: MAS53

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Green
items.body: Purchased the green and I’m in love with the color. Good quality sweater and comfortable fabric. Read more
items.author: Bear

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars LOVE LOVE LOVE
items.body: I love this sweater! It is thick, so it's great for the winter! It does stretch out a little bit, particularly in the neck. I wear it to work and will be wearing it to family thanksgiving. It can dress up or dress casual, while still wanting to look nice. The seams are great and strong. It wasn't super soft, but isn't abrasive at all. I highly recommend. Read more
items.author: Hannah

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just what I was looking for
items.body: Soft, cozy and just the right amount of warmth. It washed up nicely. I will likely buy another if a different color because I like this sweater so well! Read more

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

This piece transitions well from daytime plans to evening events with a quick change of shoes and a small bag or clutch.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Blue, Grey Blue, Apricot, Black, Camel, Coffee, Orange, Brick Red, Dark Green, Red, Rose Red, Navy, Haze Blue, Khaki. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
